column5: Hi all, Crappies are on fire, limited out in 25 minutes the other morning, nothing HUGE, but decent fish. Loved these little bug things I found at the bottom of my Gulp! assortment jar, all in 18FOW coming off the bottom. WATCH THE VIDEO @ THE LINK BELOW.https://youtu.be/Ax7q5QRBEu8
That is some quick fish action and some great eating. Congrats and Thanks for posting it.
